  "datePublished": "2014-03-18T08:05:15-04:00",
  "dateModified": "2015-03-08T22:38:51-04:00",
  "description": "No time? Hate grocery shopping? Tiny kitchen? David Spinks, cofounder of an online cooking bootcamp, shares easy, actionable tips to help you become a better home cook.
",
  "about": [
    {
      "@type": "Thing",
      "name": "Eat",
      "sameAs": "http://greatist.com/eat"
    },
