      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">No time? Hate grocery shopping? Tiny kitchen? David Spinks, cofounder of an online cooking bootcamp, shares easy, actionable tips to help you become a better home cook.
</div>
                <header class="article-header">
          <div class="group-article-meta">
            <div
  class="field field-name-post-date"
  itemprop="datePublished"
  content="2014-03-18"
>
  March 18, 2014  <span class="separator">|</span> </div>
            <div class="field article-author-top" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
  <span class="label">By </span>
